com.interpss.dc.pv.module

Interface PVModuleItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVModuleItemImpl

    public interface PVModuleItem
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'PV Model Item'. PVModuleItem has a ref to a PVModel object contained in the net. The PVModel might be shared by other items, in Volt/Amp unit. Some of the PVModel parameters, such as ShadingFactor might be overrided. Method are in per unit

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Name
    • Desc
    • Shading Factor
    • Parent
    • Pv Model
    See Also:
    PVModulePackage.getPVModuleItem()
